txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Blackened sword sheaths from the goblins east of Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'I am certain that this will bring Amarion a measure of calm. Thank you.'

'Amarion is a good man, we have all learned that...would you mind helping us cheer him up a little? He is concerned that the growing number of goblins are soon to overtake us, but if you thin the goblins' number....'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Blackened Sword Sheaths
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of blackened sword sheaths.
Deliver the blackened sword sheaths to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
Wanted: Blackened sword sheaths from the goblins east of Amon Raith.
